captions.text:
-Hi, I'm Brooklyn from
Brooklyn and Bailey.

And you guys all know
we've been moving.

And we are currently
moving right now.

But my mom just
went to California

She brought us home
a little surprise.

This one is sour
cream and onion.

But we are going to be doing
a video about our whole family

and Jenny Show Me
Cute kids we are all

going to show them eating
one of theses crickets.

Kind of tastes like a sunflower
seed-- chewy yet satisfying.

This is Bella from
Jenny Show Me Cute.

And do you want to
eat your cricket?

-Sour cream and onion,
or bacon and cheese?

-So, this is Trevor
from Jenny Show Me Cute.

So, do you want sour cream an
onion, or bacon and cheese?
Get a big nice juicy one.

-This is Jenny
from Show Me Cute.

So do you want a sour cream and
onion, or a bacon and cheese?

I'd rather do the
cheese, I think.

It does taste like a nut or
sunflower seed, or a nut.

-Sour cream and onion,
or bacon and cheese?

Sour cream and onion,
bacon and cheese.
-Oh I don't want to bite down.

-Bacon and cheese,
sour cream and onion.
Which one do you want to eat?
Do you want to eat this?

-Sour cream and onion,
bacon and cheese?

It kinda tastes like
a sunflower seed.

Sour cream and onion,
or bacon and cheese?

-Sour cream and onion
and bacon and cheese.

It's like you ate the
sunflower seed shells.

-I can smell them
on your breath.

If you guys like
sunflower seeds,

I'm pretty sure
you'll enjoy cricket.

But anyways, go
follow us at Instagram
And we will see you next week.
